{"tid":1404394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會去荃灣集會嘅同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T10:43:12.000Z","uid":103653,"like":346,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"62f3382041924e61cb0927c9350ad8b98dd259ed","tid":1404394,"uid":103653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"我見大家仲1516緊到底去荃灣公園定係沙咀道足球場<br />\n而家我為大家帶黎現場情況俾大家睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mrGySzf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmrGySzf.png&h=2912654e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jEXeB0W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjEXeB0W.png&h=260230d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESwSoFX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESwSoFX.png&h=e35060b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由上述圖片顯示可見<br />\n沙咀道足球場嘅地下係極度完整而且冇任何嘅油係需要重新畫過<br />\n再加上係公告上面係冇講到明8月5號係有任何工程<br />\n包括起辦公室旁邊嘅公告全部都冇講<br />\n兼且枱上面嘅觀眾席一眼望落去大致完整<br />\n因為太多賓賓係上面坐所以我就唔影相啦<br />\n所以我覺得8月5號返去沙咀道足球場係可行<br />\n <br />\n如果大眾嘅方向係決定轉場的話 要記得去荃灣公園通知去集會嘅人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=轉場去沙咀道<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=留喺荃灣公園"},{"pid":"00dc61bc318ef8b6b2c47dbb1953af8c44f220a9","tid":1404394,"uid":103653,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:19:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f83f03fafed0f2a02cc2c89dae2cc0b7ba05b394","tid":1404394,"uid":103653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c0cbb343e143a96973b2a21f596e670b4e7e4da","tid":1404394,"uid":103653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:20:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e9143d34cae6b3a71a00c74c9f586dd605079f5d","tid":1404394,"uid":103653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1d4effd1ba003806